name: GAM3 BOY
description: When I'm tired of playing games I always look for alternative games, one of which is to play Dino Chrome. Because esports is very popular in this digital world, I think we need a new branch of esports. One of them is this Dino Chrome game. I think it can be a great competitive game to play with friends or random people and this artwork is inspired by it, bringing an old-school feel to it
